translated:
Ygherg, Rolf Uno, lawyer, Gothenburg, born on 5/9/88 in Gothenburg, to wholesale merchant Hans Ludvig Y. and Anna Maria Hertz. Married in 1921 to Lilla Jansson. Children: Lillemor, born on 23, married to medical licentiate Bengt Kumlin, Ragnhild, born in 1945. 

Education: Graduated from Gothenburg in 1909, law degree from Uppsala in 1916. Acting notary in Göta Court of Appeal in 1918, district court service in Sunnerviken, Skånings, Vilske, Valle, Askim, Östra and Västra Hisings, and Sävedals district courts from 1918-1919. Acting notary in Gothenburg City Hall from 1920-1923. Established own law practice in Gothenburg since 1923. 

Positions: Board member of Railway Company Gothenburg-Färön since 1925. Member of the Swedish Advocate Society since 1928.
